   Richman, SK (Corresponding Author), Rocky Mt Biol Labs, Crested Butte, CO 81224 USA.
   Richman, Sarah K.; Bosak, John T.; Bronstein, Judith L., Univ Arizona, Dept Ecol \& Evolutionary Biol, Tucson, AZ 85721 USA.
   Richman, Sarah K.; Irwin, Rebecca E.; Bosak, John T.; Bronstein, Judith L., Rocky Mt Biol Labs, Crested Butte, CO 81224 USA.
   Irwin, Rebecca E., North Carolina State Univ, Dept Appl Ecol, Raleigh, NC 27695 USA.},
